            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\begin{array}{l} D i s t _ {M a x _ {m i l e s}} = E E P R O M \\_ T R I P \\_ R A N G E \\_ D I S T \\_ M A X \\_ M I L E S \\\\ \\hskip 1 4. 2 2 6 3 7 8 p t A \\text {m a x i m u m v a l u e (d i s t a n c e) t h a t m a y b e d i s p l a y e d i n u n i t s m i l e s}. \\end{array}",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
