                73,
                517,
                91
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Note that the values of "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\varnothing I F C _ { n }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "and "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\varnothing I F C _ { n - 1 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "must be stored by the instrument pack when the ignition is switched off (INTERNAL_OPERATING_MODE changes from THREE (3) to FOUR (4)) so that the output of the Range to Empty calculation is the same when the ignition is next switched on (INTERNAL_OPERATING_MODE changes from FOUR (4) or FIVE (5) to THREE (3)). "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                4,
                123,
                975,
                207
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "The Range to Empty value shall be calculated as described in the following steps: "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                4,
                212,
                742,
                232
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "1. This step depends upon the value of “Vehicle Speed”: "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                64,
                232,
                580,
                252
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "a. If “Vehicle Speed” ≥ EEPROM_TRIP_RANGE_CALC_LIMIT, then whenever a new value of “Fuel Consumption” is received it shall be used to determine the value of Calculated Average Instantaneous Fuel Consumption: "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                119,
                252,
                977,
                314
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\varnothing I F C _ {n _ {C a l c}} = \\varnothing I F C _ {n - 1} + \\left(\\frac {I F C - \\varnothing I F C _ {n - 1}}{k _ {d}}\\right)",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/82cad14c65cfc5d6a664545e1bb27f566a9d40f4f4c23870a731aa38f2a3d9ee.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                233,
                314,
                600,
                359
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "b. If “Vehicle Speed” "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "<"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "EEPROM_TRIP_RANGE_CALC_LIMIT, then any new value of “Fuel Consumption” shall be ignored and the previous value shall be used: "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                119,
                359,
                906,
                400
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\varnothing I F C _ {n _ {C a l c}} = \\varnothing I F C _ {n - 1}",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/5d6483db95f9b989808dfc8d39dfb8cbfa32fa9f1653f86cbb8dc492e61adcc8.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                235,
                400,
                425,
                425
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "i.e. "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\varnothing I F C _ { n _ { C a l c } }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "is not updated and is therefore “frozen” "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                206,
                425,
                691,
                447
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "2. This step depends upon the previous step and the constant value of "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\emptyset I F C _ { n _ { M i n } }"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                62,
                447,
                799,
                470
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "a. If the previous step has resulted in the re-use of the previous value, this step shall also be ignored: "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                119,
                472,
                959,
                511
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\varnothing I F C _ {n} = \\varnothing I F C _ {n _ {C a l c}} = \\varnothing I F C _ {n - 1}",
                "math_type": "latex",
